  "body": "In the library Address.sol, there is a function sendValue(), which has the require statement, where `address(this).balance >= amount` noted. What if the balance of the contract is exactly equal to the amount? In this case, it will be reverted with the message \"Address: insufficient balance\", which is not true or am I missing something? \r\n\r\nLink to the function: \r\nhttps://github.com/OpenZeppelin/openzeppelin-contracts/blob/6e8d885ca71584659ad728411832840cf0bf507b/contracts/utils/Address.sol#L60-L65\r\n\r\nHuge thanks!",
